Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.60,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Hello,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:43.62,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:08:10.52,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,I am Nakashima Yuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:10:00.42,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Welcome to ProSeka AfterTalk "Unsteady, still steady step" Edition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:06.91,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,This is Yuki Nakashima, voice of Shiho Hinomori from Leo/need!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:12.67,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,In this edition of ProSeka AfterTalk, we'll look back at this event while covering messages you, the fans, have sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:16.09,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,This time, we'll be covering the "Unsteady, still steady step" event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:19.42,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Ah, thank God I said it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.42,0:10:20.97,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,When I first saw the script, I was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:25.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"...Unsteady, still steady step.... There's way too many 'st's here."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:29.06,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"Is this supposed to be a tongue-twister?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:34.14,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Right, so did you enjoy this event's story, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:37.59,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Yep, I sure did read it right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:39.88,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"{\i1}Kon-needo{\i0}". {\i1}Kon-needo{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.63,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,It's like a "st st" party up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:47.77,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Yeah but like,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:50.48,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,talking about the story for real,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:54.17,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,it's not like there were any earthshattering developments or decisions here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:11:00.60,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Honami was just a little uncertain on this decision in front of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:07.11,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,{\i1}But{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:09.62,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"I liked the story!" Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:11.64,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Glad to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.58,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,We've had a bit of a mini-renewal for AfterTalk since April
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.58,0:11:20.22,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,We've gathered the comments you sent in through email and the Discord submissions channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:22.16,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Thanks for all the messages, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:26.59,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,We'd like to go over some of them in our program today, so please look forward to that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:28.79,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Also, if you have any thoughts on today's program,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:31.85,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,please post them on X with #ProSekaAfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:36.42,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,We'll also be watching the YouTube chat, so please keep all the messages coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:42.25,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Also, note that since the mini-renewal, we won't be watching the AfterLives. Thanks for your understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:47.49,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Yeah, they're going to have to start choosing now that they're pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:52.53,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"Shindo-san helped out a ton." For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:56.77,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I remember that part where he's on the phone with her — how to say —
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.38,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,the splitscreen part?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:02.78,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,When it shows Honami and Shindo-san side by side,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:05.01,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,it makes Shindo's frame look even bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.01,0:12:05.94,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I saw it and was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:10.94,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"ah, that sure is a fully grown man."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.80,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"The AfterLive was really good!" Mmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:14.75,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:19.88,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Alright! Let's get right into the "Unsteady, still steady step" story...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:23.49,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,There really are way too many "st st"s.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:25.00,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Hard to keep a straight face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.66,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Let's get into the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:31.17,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Let's look back together while going over some of the messages you've sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.90,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,First up, a message from "King"-san. Thank you for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:36.48,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"{\i1}Kon-needo{\i0}, Nakashima-san!" {\i1}Kon-needo{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.48,0:12:42.35,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"I was really glad to see Leo/need growing more as pros in this story."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:47.78,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"Both the one-man live and the fan fes were big opportunities for Leo/need to move forward."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:51.82,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"There wasn't a clear right option so it was tough deciding which to write a new song for."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:56.74,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"I'm pretty indecisive myself and tend to freeze from over-analysis,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:59.32,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,so I was really able to sympathize with Honami."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:04.99,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"By the way, Nakashima-san, when you're faced with important choices, how do you generally come to a decision?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.24,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Thank you for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:09.03,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Ehhhhhh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:12.64,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I think usually,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:16.31,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I'm able to come up with a pretty clear option I favor more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:20.74,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,But if it were like the story, where I wanted to do both things...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:22.66,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I'd probably try to do both.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:27.78,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,But if it were a {\i1}real{\i0} scheduling conflict, like on the exact same day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.87,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,like I had other work scheduled on the same day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.75,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I'd just have to choose one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.19,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,But if it were like the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:41.34,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,like if I needed to get two separate things done by the same day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:44.79,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I think I'd try to do both.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:49.30,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Like, it definitely depends on what exactly I'm deciding on,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:52.22,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,but I tend to make decisions really impulsively like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.18,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Oh yeah and of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.74,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I usually just go by vibes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:14:00.53,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,So I can't really be of much help. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.03,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Actually, what would you all do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:08.32,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Yeah. "If I could swing both, I'd definitely do it."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:12.77,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,As uh... selfish as that would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.77,0:14:13.65,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:17.07,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Would probably try something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:20.81,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Leave it up to vibes. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:23.41,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"Flip a coin." Haha maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:27.07,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I mean if you're really stuck between the two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:29.65,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Like if you don't want to regret your decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:34.48,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,and you really can't decide on a clear favorite, maybe leaving it up to fate makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:38.25,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Play "eeny, meeny, miny, moe" or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:44.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,That sure is one way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:45.83,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,But I mean, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:50.40,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,if it really were a "one or the other" situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:53.50,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I think I'd just go with vibes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:55.93,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Like just going with whatever my gut was telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:15:01.90,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Even if I were just feeling it 1-2% more, I'd probably go with that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:02.66,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:06.48,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,If I were in Leo/need's specific situation in the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:12.56,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,and the request for the fan fes got withdrawn,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:14.86,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I'd actually be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:18.39,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I'd be like "Oh! We get to do both!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:22.81,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Probably not good to think this way but I'd be like "we got lucky!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:25.81,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Mmm. Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:28.91,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Okay. Let's move on to one more message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:31.68,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Next up, from "Copy"-san. Thank you for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.74,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"Yukki, {\i1}kon-needo{\i0}." {\i1}Kon-needo{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:39.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"I was really excited to see Leo/need finally getting an opportunity to do their much-awaited one-man live."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:44.05,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"I was secretly hoping that they would do that instrument shuffle for the real thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:46.05,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Thank you for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:47.96,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Oh yeah. Would definitely want to see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:51.10,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Ehhhh? Like,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.16,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I, uh, I don't really think I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:16:00.14,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,If I really had to do that, I'd be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:05.06,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I wonder... Shiho switched from bass,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:09.84,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,and had to play drums... or guitar, or keyboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:13.68,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Would you even be able to get her to do it? That's what I'd be wondering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:16.73,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I mean, if it were for rehearsal, I think she would be okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:23.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,As someone so talented and self-confident in her music,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:27.58,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I think she'd have some pride on the line! Even if it were just for an MC, she'd be like "I'm not giving you my bass."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:30.65,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,That being said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:33.54,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,{\i1}I{\i0} definitely would want to see that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.54,0:16:37.20,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Seeing her get flustered like that... that'd be really fun to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:43.06,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,But yeah, I kind of wanna see everyone go "how do you play this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:48.49,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I for sure could watch that forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:51.49,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Hope we get that one day. Curious what exactly would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:55.07,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,But yeah, I'm interested in where the story will go from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:59.10,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"I can't imagine Shiho-chan on the drums." Ahh, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:02.75,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Hmm, I don't know, she seems good at keeping rhythm though,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:06.56,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,so I feel like she might be able to keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:10.23,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,But your hands and feet are doing different things,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.49,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,so she might end up a little flustered too. I'm really curious though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.49,0:17:15.81,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"I'd wanna see her on guitar!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.06,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Mmmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.07,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,That would be cool to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:24.67,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"Everyone going 'how do you play this?' would be so cute." Oh yeah. 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.05,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Ah, that would be so great to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:32.58,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,So yeah, everyone, definitely look forward to the coming stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:35.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Thank you for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:43.61,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Alright, I've picked a scene from the story I'd like to talk about, so let's watch it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:45.98,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,This time, I chose Chapter 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.28,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Here we go!
Comment: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:50.28,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,~~~START STORY WATCHALONG~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:55.10,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Nakashima-san, could you play guitar when you started learning bass?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:55.63,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.24,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I gave up on guitar pretty quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:08.40,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}She understands how both sides of the audience feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:14.05,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Speaking of Hona-chan as a leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:20.75,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}asking from the perspective of, "which one will make our fans the happiest?",
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:24.64,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}and actually going out of her way to understand everyone's perspective,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:31.34,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I think that's incredible. Shows her determination as a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:58.45,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It's impressive that she realizes she needs to decide this based on her own feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:01.85,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}but also realizing she can't keep everyone waiting forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:26.05,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Chapter 7 was also really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:44.92,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Overthinking makes it tougher to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:14.08,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Ah, it's that scene I mentioned laughing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:17.41,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Shindo-san's very large manly frame here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:20.41,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I was like "woah".
Comment: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:21.31,Shiho,,0,0,0,card,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:57.19,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:35.29,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Good for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.29,0:21:38.01,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}This is an amazing opportunity for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.24,0:22:14.47,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}This happens, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:18.18,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Super realistic scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:24:00.09,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It's okay to feel relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.94,0:24:05.51,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Hona-chan is such a good girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.56,0:24:38.32,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}You're already such a good leader!
Comment: 0,0:24:43.98,0:24:46.98,Note,,0,0,0,human,~~~END STORY WATCHALONG~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.92,0:24:52.05,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,That was Chapter 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.05,0:25:00.83,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,So my favorite, or most memorable part was that part just before,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.83,0:25:03.46,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,when Honami was thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.46,0:25:09.28,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"I thought for sure I'd be able to come to a decision,"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.28,0:25:11.92,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,and was feeling a little disappointed in herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.92,0:25:15.68,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,but then resolving herself to continue being a strong leader for Leo/need.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.68,0:25:19.05,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,That was really memorable for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.19,0:25:24.21,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,If I were in her shoes, I'd probably just blow it off like,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.21,0:25:27.55,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"oh, yay!~"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.55,0:25:32.59,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,A lot of that has to do with the fact that I've never really worked as a leader myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.59,0:25:36.18,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,but that said... how to say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.18,0:25:44.31,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I definitely feel that Honami is super dependable and responsible,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.31,0:25:49.12,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,but at the same time, I kept hoping that things wouldn't get too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.12,0:25:55.73,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I was worried that Honami-chan might panic if she really did have to make that tough decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.73,0:25:58.65,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,So that was our scene for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.04,0:26:07.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,This time, the offer was almost withdrawn, but then they were told they could have a slot...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.02,0:26:17.84,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,You might feel lucky, but if it was withdrawn without a second chance, you'd definitely regret not speaking up sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.48,0:26:21.34,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Decisions like that are really difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.34,0:26:28.16,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,But there are many times in life when you have to make those kinds of choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.16,0:26:33.44,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,I'm not sure how Honami will make her choices from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.44,0:26:37.50,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,or what kind of path Leo/need will take,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.50,0:26:41.75,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,but I want to keep watching over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.75,0:26:43.64,Shiho,,0,0,0,,And I pray...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.64,0:26:45.94,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,I pray they don't end up on bad terms,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.94,0:26:50.90,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,or have their mental health suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.52,0:26:56.32,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,I honestly don't know what kind of story is waiting for us either.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.36,0:27:05.28,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Oh yeah, Project Sekai event stories always leave some kind of foreshadowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.08,0:27:08.32,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,I mean, of course they do, since the story'll continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.84,0:27:12.03,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Of course it'll continue, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.00,0:27:15.16,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Yukki, give some of that chill energy to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.04,0:27:19.51,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Well, hold on a sec, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.44,0:27:22.92,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,They're still high school students, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.92,0:27:25.96,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,This is when they {\i1}should{\i0} be worrying a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.96,0:27:30.30,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,and learning a looot from their failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.92,0:27:34.77,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.77,0:27:35.29,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.29,0:27:39.64,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,That said, there was one more scene that caught my eye personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.64,0:27:44.82,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,It was in Episode 7, and we also saw it a bit in Episode 8,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.82,0:27:51.42,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,but I really liked the part in Episode 7 where Honami and Ichika go to see the Miku concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.42,0:27:53.88,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Ichika was more excited than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.88,0:27:56.80,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,She was all like "Yay! It's Miku!"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.80,0:27:58.15,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,I thought it was so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.08,0:28:01.44,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,I thought about featuring that part too,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.40,0:28:09.40,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,but if I did, I'd just be like "wow, Ichi cute. Hona cute. Crowd members cute."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.64,0:28:12.03,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,So I just went with Episode 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.88,0:28:16.24,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,But Episode 7 was really cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.68,0:28:19.12,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,"I kinda wanna watch it again."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.12,0:28:22.26,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,By all means, please go back and read it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.26,0:28:24.60,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,That Miku live part was super adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.12,0:28:27.56,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,I want to go to a Miku live too!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.56,0:28:28.92,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.56,0:28:34.92,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Actually, back when the title was still "MikuPa,"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.92,0:28:38.05,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,I'm originally from Wakayama, and there happened to be a live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.05,0:28:40.20,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,I was just as excited as Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.20,0:28:41.54,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,I was like, "It's Miku-chan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.54,0:28:42.41,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,"Miku!"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.01,0:28:44.96,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,I was super hyped for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.55,0:28:49.30,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,I hope everyone gets a chance to be as excited as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.30,0:28:51.52,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Anyway, I got a bit sidetracked again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.52,0:28:55.80,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's take a look at the card illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.80,0:29:01.86,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,First, I'll share some comments from the illustration team about the outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.06,0:29:09.20,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,This story was about Honami realizing the importance and weight of making decisions as a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.20,0:29:12.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,While the story showed her struggling with the weight of her decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.02,0:29:16.95,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,the illustrations reflect a positive determination to find the best path forward for Leo/need.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.95,0:29:19.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Combining that with the event song's rhythmic energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.02,0:29:22.24,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,the outfit design conveys a lighthearted "keep moving forward" attitude.
Comment: 0,0:29:22.24,0:29:27.00,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,[WIP] check these translation
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.24,0:29:27.00,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,And since this song features a sweet cuteness we don't always see from Leo/need,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.00,0:29:32.72,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,we used pop and cute design elements like colorful star patterns and sneakers as the motif for our design.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.72,0:29:36.78,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Also, to symbolize Leo/need choosing their path as a band,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.78,0:29:41.06,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,each of the three has a star chart-like element in their outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.06,0:29:45.72,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,We also incorporated items where the color palette is meant to resemble a compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.40,0:29:51.40,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,This palette represents not only the choice between Leo/need's new song and Miku's song,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.40,0:29:59.46,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,but also the many choices that they will have to make in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.46,0:30:00.32,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.56,0:30:04.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Alright, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.02,0:30:05.02,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Who should we start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.56,0:30:07.44,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Who should we look at first?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.44,0:30:10.48,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Do we usually start with the 4-stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.48,0:30:12.31,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Let's start with the 4-stars then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.83,0:30:13.70,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Here's Honami.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.70,0:30:18.36,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}This is from that scene in Episode 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.36,0:30:20.24,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}This is the untrained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.24,0:30:25.42,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Hmm. Honami has a bit of a stunned look here,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.42,0:30:28.84,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}{\i1}but{\i0} her smartphone case is super soothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.84,0:30:34.28,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Is that a Shiba Inu?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.28,0:30:36.40,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It looks like one. Very comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.00,0:30:39.44,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}And here's the trained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.44,0:30:40.91,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.12,0:30:44.62,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It's kind of a portrait shot, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.62,0:30:49.03,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It looks really good if you turn it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.36,0:30:55.54,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Now that I think about it, Leo/need hasn't really had anything this pop and cute yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.80,0:30:59.00,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Oh yeah, and the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.00,0:31:01.20,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}So many stars all over the art.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.84,0:31:05.27,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}And look, there's a dog on that building signboard in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.24,0:31:09.80,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Oh yeah, and she has a compass on the bag too.
Comment: 0,0:31:09.80,0:31:10.96,Shiho,,0,0,0,card,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.80,0:31:10.96,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}So stylish!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.92,0:31:17.08,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}So, that was the Honami trained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.08,0:31:19.76,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Wait, that's an apple badge, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.32,0:31:20.96,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Cute~
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.96,0:31:23.07,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.44,0:31:27.43,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Moving on... to Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.24,0:31:30.60,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Ichika's trained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.60,0:31:32.63,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}This was from Episode 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.91,0:31:39.71,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Ichika was telling Honami not to sweat it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.41,0:31:44.46,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}And here is the trained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.46,0:31:45.86,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Wow~
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.00,0:31:52.27,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I'm losing my vocabulary here. All I've been saying is "so good".
Comment: 0,0:31:54.20,0:31:58.52,Shiho,,0,0,0,card,[WIP] Check translation
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.20,0:31:58.52,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I love how you kind of get a full view of the scenery for Ichika's card here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.16,0:32:04.38,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}And the way she's sitting with her knees up and her guitar on her back looks nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.88,0:32:09.22,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I call it '{\i1}sankaku-zuwari{\i0}' (triangle sitting).
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.22,0:32:11.09,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It's called '{\i1}taiiku-zuwari{\i0} (gym sitting)?' Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.68,0:32:13.47,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}My regional dialect is showing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.16,0:32:17.61,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Is '{\i1}sankaku-zuwari{\i0}' just a Kansai thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.20,0:32:19.44,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}You've never heard it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.44,0:32:20.72,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}No?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.72,0:32:21.88,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.88,0:32:22.62,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}You haven't?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.62,0:32:23.80,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}'{\i1}Sankaku-zuwari{\i0}'—you haven't?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.80,0:32:25.20,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Sorry, I meant '{\i1}taiiku-zuwari{\i0},' then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.92,0:32:31.15,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}That was a dialect thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.15,0:32:32.47,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.92,0:32:35.84,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Doesn't sitting like that feel a bit 'student-like'?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.44,0:32:39.36,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}You don't really sit like that once you're an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.36,0:32:41.32,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Maybe only during photoshoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.08,0:32:47.28,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Like, if they tell you to sit there like a student, you might do it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.48,0:32:53.42,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I'm being told '{\i1}taiiku-zuwari{\i0}' is standard, but '{\i1}sankaku-zuwari{\i0}' is Kansai-only.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.42,0:32:54.32,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.32,0:32:55.00,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}My mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.72,0:32:59.88,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Anyway, I personally really like that student vibe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.36,0:33:04.59,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Also, the background... there are so many instruments!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.25,0:33:05.75,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.28,0:33:08.08,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.72,0:33:13.56,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}There's a guitar, a bass, an acoustic guitar...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.56,0:33:16.62,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}and you can even see some drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.62,0:33:18.23,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.35,0:33:20.60,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}That was Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.60,0:33:22.48,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Next is Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.28,0:33:25.72,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Untrained Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.36,0:33:29.36,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}She's all excited for the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.60,0:33:31.42,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}That's our Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.42,0:33:34.26,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Leo/need Rin is so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.26,0:33:37.16,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I really love how she's overflowing with that 'gyaru' vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.72,0:33:39.98,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Wow~
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.98,0:33:44.60,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}And that paper necklace... she definitely made that herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.60,0:33:49.32,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It's like in class, remember? You'd always put those up on the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.44,0:33:51.76,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Good times.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.84,0:33:55.26,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}And are those loose socks?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.26,0:33:57.96,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}That's another great touch. It really adds to the gyaru feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.64,0:34:00.14,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}And here's the trained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.14,0:34:00.76,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.64,0:34:05.50,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.50,0:34:09.76,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}This really captures all of Rin's...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.76,0:34:11.44,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.80,0:34:16.24,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I love that she's wearing a sleeveless top underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.32,0:34:21.70,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}And the uhh... what do you call this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.70,0:34:23.12,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}The thing on the side of the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.12,0:34:26.12,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I love that she's balancing on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.12,0:34:28.16,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It's so like Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.16,0:34:31.80,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I wanna be like "don't swing your guitar around!"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.80,0:34:33.84,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}"You're gonna get hurt!"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.16,0:34:37.12,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}And the loose socks again are cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.64,0:34:39.99,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Trends always come back around.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.44,0:34:42.64,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Super cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.64,0:34:44.48,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}And that ribbon is just adorable too.
Comment: 0,0:34:44.48,0:34:45.32,Shiho,,0,0,0,card,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.48,0:34:46.14,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It suits her so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.08,0:34:50.72,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Ah... So cute I can't help but just sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.64,0:34:53.80,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Now for Shiho...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.80,0:34:55.20,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Shiho's trained art.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.20,0:34:56.20,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}THIS ART THOUGH
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.70,0:34:58.36,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}THANK YOU SO MUCH
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.08,0:35:00.96,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Thank you for drawing such a lovely illustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.96,0:35:02.54,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It makes me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.54,0:35:03.92,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I could just spin around.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.84,0:35:08.00,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.61,0:35:09.37,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Hold on—
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.32,0:35:15.88,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I can see myself spinning because of the delay,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.12,0:35:19.92,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Ahh, so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.60,0:35:21.24,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.84,0:35:25.24,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}But isn't this so good though?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.24,0:35:27.02,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}She looks a bit sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.02,0:35:28.84,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Maybe she slept too much the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.84,0:35:30.88,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}She looks so sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.88,0:35:31.80,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}{\i1}Ahh{\i0}, so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.00,0:35:34.64,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Super duper cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.64,0:35:41.20,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Plus, on the wall in the back, is that a photo from the autumn shuffle event?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.20,0:35:42.80,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}That's a nice touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.80,0:35:44.65,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Ah, I should be looking here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.80,0:35:48.04,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}This is really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.04,0:35:54.58,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I'm happy I can see so many little details of Shiho's room like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.58,0:35:56.81,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}and even the soles of her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.04,0:36:01.48,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Usually, they're wearing shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.04,0:36:04.32,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}so you don't get a chance to look at their feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.92,0:36:09.84,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Seeing the soles of a character's feet, especially a 2D one,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.84,0:36:11.80,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}is actually kind of nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.80,0:36:12.84,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}What am I even saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.40,0:36:18.40,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Am I a creep?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.16,0:36:20.36,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Someone's gonna chew me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.00,0:36:22.16,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Maybe the devs.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.16,0:36:24.28,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}"Please don't look at that stuff!"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.28,0:36:26.75,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Then don't draw it in the first place, honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.68,0:36:31.39,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}They'll ask me what's wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.44,0:36:34.68,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}No, no, I'm just overflowing with love.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.68,0:36:36.58,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}And that was only the untrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.58,0:36:38.28,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Let's look at the trained art too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.28,0:36:39.20,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Oh, it went back.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.12,0:36:43.35,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Here's the trained. Very nice~
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.20,0:36:45.76,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.24,0:36:49.04,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}That varsity jacket looks so good on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.40,0:36:55.80,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Also, I feel like you don't see her with an iced tea drink like that too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.44,0:36:58.54,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Wait, maybe it's apple tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.54,0:36:59.52,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I have a feeling it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.52,0:37:03.47,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Wow... I didn't know Shiho drank stuff like apple tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.72,0:37:07.96,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It really gives off that vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.08,0:37:10.28,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.96,0:37:18.76,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}And it looks like she's in front of a music store. Fits her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.60,0:37:26.66,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Also, Shiho's character color is light green,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.66,0:37:30.74,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}so her apple bag being green is a great touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.74,0:37:32.20,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It's so good. Oh crap—
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.20,0:37:33.51,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I almost spun around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.20,0:37:35.60,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I was about to spin again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.60,0:37:36.92,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.16,0:37:40.38,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}And finally... MEIKO.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.38,0:37:43.82,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}This is MEIKO's 2-star card.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.82,0:37:45.02,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Wow~
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.02,0:37:49.66,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}When MEIKO wears the varsity jacket, it's a completely different vibe,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.66,0:37:52.84,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}She looks so much more mature. It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.56,0:37:54.50,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.82,0:38:01.76,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Leo/need.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.04,0:37:59.12,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}The logo on the sleeve is great too. I want that logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.12,0:38:00.82,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}And that logo— I need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.76,0:38:03.86,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}That "LN" logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.86,0:38:06.40,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It'd be cool if they'd make it into merch so I could get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.84,0:38:09.80,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}"Spin as many times as you like."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.80,0:38:11.07,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}It's too embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.08,0:38:17.60,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}You usually do these AfterTalks alone, at your own pace,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.60,0:38:23.48,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}so I end up acting like my usual self, which is embarrassing to watch later.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.88,0:38:31.34,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Even though this is an official PJSK stream, I just go at my own pace,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.34,0:38:36.87,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}so sometimes I'm like "is this really okay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.88,0:38:39.24,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I'm so sorry, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.20,0:38:42.24,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}But I really want that Leo/need logo though.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.24,0:38:44.92,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}I want them to release it as a patch or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.52,0:38:47.76,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Please make it happen someday, higher-ups.
Comment: 0,0:38:47.76,0:38:48.98,Shiho,,0,0,0,card,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.76,0:38:48.98,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Please and thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.98,0:38:52.23,Shiho - Card,,0,0,0,card,{\pos(650,750)}Anyway, that's all for the card illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.92,0:39:01.95,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Next, let's watch the 2DMV for 'Transparent Palette,' the song for this event commissioned from aqu3ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.95,0:39:05.44,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,Then, we'll talk a bit about the song itself and the MV.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.44,0:39:09.90,Shiho,,0,0,0,autosub,So without further ado, released just yesterday, here's the 2DMV!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.90,0:39:10.71,Shiho,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Comment: 0,0:42:17.27,0:42:19.20,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,~~~START SONG TALK~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.27,0:42:19.55,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Waaah~
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.03,0:42:21.55,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Great MV.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.55,0:42:24.92,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,It has a feeling of, how to say, lightness and transparency,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.92,0:42:26.82,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,while also keeping a pop vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.82,0:42:28.75,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.75,0:42:34.66,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,I remember when I recorded for this song,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.66,0:42:36.38,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Even though it's pretty upbeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.38,0:42:43.64,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,I remember being asked to sing with a bit of hesitation in the verse and prechorus.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.64,0:42:46.94,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Almost like I was a bit worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.94,0:42:49.74,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,And then in the chorus, how to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.74,0:42:54.37,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,we were asked to sing with a much brighter and transparent feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.37,0:42:57.06,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,so that's how the song turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.06,0:43:02.90,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Also, I love the part of the lyrics that says "and on days of celebration, we'll have apple pies" so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.90,0:43:08.34,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Actually, as far as commissioned song lyrics go,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.34,0:43:11.78,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,And seeing a character's favorite food directly mentioned like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.78,0:43:15.14,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,I don't remember if that's happened yet. Is this the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.14,0:43:17.44,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,That's what immediately stood out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.44,0:43:21.76,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Yeah. It's a pretty new feeling. And makes it easy to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.76,0:43:25.64,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,I remember that part being stuck in my head forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.64,0:43:28.05,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,But a good kind of "stuck in my head". I really liked it.
