Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.20,0:43:38.29,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Giant one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.58,0:43:44.11,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,When I first played it, I was like "woah, is than an apple pie?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.11,0:43:47.55,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Definitely try out the Master chart if you wanna see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.08,0:43:51.59,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,"You think Shiho's ramen will show up one day?"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.59,0:43:53.36,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.36,0:43:55.74,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Would Shiho get...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.74,0:43:57.85,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Would she get a pop song like this though?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.00,0:44:02.60,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,I mean, {\i1}I'd{\i0} definitely be interested in seeing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.64,0:44:07.56,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Yeah, try the Master chart. It's uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.56,0:44:12.13,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,You can, uh... they made it so you can play Master mode immediately now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.13,0:44:14.26,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,So do try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.26,0:44:17.29,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,I can't imagine Shiho and ramen in a song like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.86,0:44:23.07,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,I think they should have a little fun with the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.07,0:44:24.80,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Like maybe she could get a metal song.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.80,0:44:25.99,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Kind of like "JYA JYA JYA",
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.99,0:44:28.55,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,or like "DA DO DO DAN DO" hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.84,0:44:34.06,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,If that really happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.06,0:44:36.22,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,I'd be a bit worried. If that really did happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.22,0:44:39.57,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,just make it an April Fool's song if you're really gonna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.26,0:44:46.75,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,"Would have lots of slap bass." Yeah, I suppose it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.93,0:44:50.27,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,"The steam from the ramen would zig zag everywhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.27,0:44:54.86,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Wow, everyone's already got so many creative ideas for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.12,0:45:03.85,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Really though, I'm excited for any potential favorite food inclusions in upcoming songs like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.85,0:45:08.11,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,And getting to see Saki's outfit here in the MV was also really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.11,0:45:14.41,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,That heart mark here is actually different for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.41,0:45:16.84,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,It's a super duper cute 2DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.84,0:45:18.67,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Please check it out, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.67,0:45:23.90,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,The 2DMV is already uploaded to the official ProSeka YouTube channel, so be sure to watch it there.
Comment: 0,0:45:18.67,0:45:23.90,Shiho,,0,0,0,song,~~~END STORY TALK~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.90,0:45:27.42,Shiho - Song,,0,0,0,song,Well then, it was just a short episode this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.42,0:45:33.20,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,but that's all we have for the "Unsteady, still steady step" AfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.20,0:45:34.53,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,So quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.73,0:45:38.16,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,That just flew by so quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.16,0:45:40.00,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,It's already 9PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.00,0:45:45.21,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I saw the clock when I spun around, I was like "crap, it's already 9?"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.21,0:45:49.39,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,I was like "I can't just be spinning here, we need to move on to watch the MV!"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.48,0:45:53.90,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,That really did fly by.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.90,0:45:56.09,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"Let's do this again!" Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.87,0:45:59.65,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"But I just got here!" Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.65,0:46:02.80,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,"Don't go, keep chatting." Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.80,0:46:09.40,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,So with that, if you haven't watched the "Unsteady, still steady step" event story yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.40,0:46:15.46,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,after the next event starts, you can read it in-game in the "Event Story" section under the "Story" button, so please do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.46,0:46:18.19,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,We'll be accepting submissions for future AfterTalks as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.19,0:46:25.06,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,You can submit your messages in the submissions channel on the official Project Sekai Discord, or through email.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.06,0:46:28.89,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Feel free to send them in after the next AfterTalk event starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.89,0:46:32.54,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,Please keep your messages related to the events.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.54,0:46:35.02,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,With that, thanks so much for a fun AfterTalk today!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.02,0:46:37.18,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,See you again next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.18,0:46:41.33,Shiho,,0,0,0,human,{\fad(0,500)}Bye bye!
